Package de.fhb.sailboat.control.navigator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Navigator
    Interface for executing a Task.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeatWorker
    Implements a beat behavior.
    NavigatorImpl
    Implementation of Navigator which calculates commands based on the Task to execute.
    ReachCircleWorker
    Calculates the relative angle from the current position to the goal defined in the task to execute and hands it over to the pilot.
    ReachPolygonWorker
    Calculates the relative angle from the current position to the centroid of the polygon defined in the task to be executed and hands it over to the pilot.
    WorkerThread<T extends Task>
    Base class for navigation threads.
